{"type": "article", "id": 22514, "title": "拼接式的小清新沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-19T07:10:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152150IKU4YS1qRWk3zvB9.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">瑞典设计品牌 Swedese 和设计师 Roger Persson 发布了一组模块化的家具，分为正方形或者正圆形两种沙发坐垫，都可以随意拼起来。在选色上使用了黄、蓝、绿、棕等自然的颜色，带给人格外的清新自然。正方形的沙发可以拼成一个大的坐垫组，其中有一块是橡木桌面，而圆形坐垫像是分散在其中的绿叶。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152148Ti56CIe0LsPKvStG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152148kRQYjbK3Ozw6SyUx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152149Br6DwPmJyjiWh04f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152149ApzUxhCsZLwFEqNu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152150WQcwM7A1rquai9Zk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}